First Technology and Dell Technologies have partnered with MyBroadband to promote their survey on enterprise-grade storage. If you complete this survey, you could win R2,000 in cash. This survey will investigate whether businesses are making use of storage arrays, as well as whether their existing storage solutions are capable of managing their workloads. This includes determining if these storage solutions support the hybrid cloud, allow for the monitoring and analysis of all environments, and provide sufficient performance. To enter the competition, follow the steps below. Standard competition rules apply.